videos.headline: Princeton Outlasts Harvard, 72-67, in Ivy Madness Semifinal Game  - Via Ivy League
videos.description: Abby Meyers contributed 22 points and Ellie Mitchell grabbed 16 rebounds to secure Princeton a spot in the Ivy Madness championship game.
